    <item>
      <title>现货黄金首次升至每盎司 2,200 美元以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/spot-gold-rises-to-2-200-an-ounce-for-the-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储维持今年降息三个季度的预期后，金价首次突破每盎司 2,200 美元，这表明他们并未对近期通胀上升感到震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/spot-gold-rises-to-2-200-an-ounce-for-the-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 22:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Trial Holdings 将在日本今年最大规模的 IPO 后首次亮相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trial-holdings-set-to-debut-after-japan-s-largest-ipo-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[折扣店连锁运营商 Trial Holdings Inc. 将于周四在东京首次公开募股，筹集了 388.5 亿日元（2.56 亿美元）的资金，这是日本今年规模最大的一次首次公开募股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trial-holdings-set-to-debut-after-japan-s-largest-ipo-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IVP的Wilhelm：对退出持谨慎乐观态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-20/ivp-s-wilhelm-cautiously-optimistic-about-exits-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[IVP 正寻求利用人工智能带来的技术变革所带来的“巨大机遇”，并推出第 18 支基金，筹集 16 亿美元资金。 IVP 普通合伙人 Cack Wilhelm 讨论了这只新基金的目标以及今年的风险投资和退出情况。她与卡罗琳·海德和埃德·勒德洛一起参与“彭博科技”节目。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-20/ivp-s-wilhelm-cautiously-optimistic-about-exits-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 20:46:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能增长有助于增强收入预测，美光股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/micron-soars-after-ai-opportunity-helps-bolster-revenue-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的计算机存储芯片制造商美光科技公司(Micron Technology Inc.)在人工智能硬件需求的提振下，对本季度的收入做出了令人惊讶的强劲预测，随后股价在尾盘上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/micron-soars-after-ai-opportunity-helps-bolster-revenue-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 20:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储坚持降息前景，新兴资产上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/emerging-market-currencies-extend-losses-before-fed-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，较高的通胀预测不会破坏今年的降息计划，从而提振了风险情绪，新兴市场资产上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/emerging-market-currencies-extend-losses-before-fed-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 10:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储决定后亚洲市场可能会出现缓解性反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-rate-hike-unlikely-to-derail-stock-rally-strategists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师和策略师表示，亚洲股市和货币似乎将对美联储的政策决定做出积极反应，美联储维持今年三次降息的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-rate-hike-unlikely-to-derail-stock-rally-strategists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 04:42:24 GMT</pubDate>
